        "timestamp": "2018-01-19 20:36:33.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nWould you mind removing the changes to SshJcraftWrapper.java in the commit? We have another commit pending (https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/28659/3) which is completely removing the DebugLog from this file, in order to match the onap logging standards.",
