        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-01-19 20:41:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nWe are trying to move all logging into the EELF, as per the onap standards. This means we want to move away from other logging frameworks such as DebugLog\nhttps://wiki.onap.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=20087036 (Logging Standards)\nhttps://jira.onap.org/browse/APPC-423 (Logging Epic)",
        "patchset_number": 2
